{"tid":1026593,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶湧現大量 Apex Legends「新食雞」作弊外掛！開發商或將實施特殊對策應對","createTime":"2019-02-18T08:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T09:27:13.000Z","uid":51464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9018e507e38d0666a778255b23a897f0dbb31b7b","tid":1026593,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"由於《PUBG（絕地求生）》與《Fortnite（堡壘之夜）》等「食雞」類大逃殺遊戲極為成功，不少遊戲廠商也劍指「食雞」電競遊戲市場。由 Respawn Entertainment 開發和 EA 發行的《Apex Legends》，正是目前最巨人氣的新款「食雞」電競遊戲，該遊戲的 Twitch 直播觀看人數，幾乎長期維持在 10 萬人以上。不過，遊戲火熱也掀起了外掛問題，淘寶更成為了《Apex Legends》的外掛集中地。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2272927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2272927&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=f18ae1d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2272927</a><br />\n======================================<br />\n仙魔大戰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ea222adac70c1c7461306ee050034e3512391b","tid":1026593,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:27:13.000Z","msg":"EA game點會冇外掛"}]}